# Exploration: paste

## Rounds
  round 0: 19 isolated cumulative, 6 identical in round (discovery)
  round 1: 19 isolated cumulative, 6 identical in round (refinement)

## Distinguished: 3/3 flags
  3 solo (unique behavior)

Aliases: -d = --delimiters, -s = --serial, -z = --zero-terminated

## Solo (unique behavior)
  -d  # reuse characters from LIST instead of TABs
  -s  # paste one file at a time instead of in parallel
  -z  # line delimiter is NUL, not newline

